ObjectStates.Name: Infinite_Bag
ObjectStates.Description: A limitless bag of success tokens.

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Dice
ContainedObjects.Description:
This dice is rolled as instructed on your action card.

Weapon - Each weapon symbol represents 1 success.

Shield - Each shield blocks 1 point of monster damage from monsters in your engagement zone.

Sun - Critical success, take a success token and re-roll the dice. Re-roll for each subsequent critical success.

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Dice
ContainedObjects.Description:
This dice is rolled for every enemy in your engagement area when performing an action.

Blank - No effect

Claws - Receive damage equal to that of the highest attack in your engagement zone reduced by number of shields.

Skull - Resolve the nemesis effect located on the nemesis card.
